last_episode_to_air.overview: Sandugo is a 2019 Philippine drama television series starring Aljur Abrenica and Ejay Falcon. The series aired on ABS-CBN's Kapamilya Gold afternoon block and worldwide on The Filipino Channel from September 30, 2019 to March 20, 2020, replacing Precious Hearts Romances Presents: Los Bastardos.
